title: Devil's Knot
description: The Arkansas town of West Memphis makes national headlines when three teenagers are arrested for the brutal murders of three little boys. Based on true events and the novel by Mara Leveritt. (2013)
description2: The Arkansas town of West Memphis makes national headlines when three teenagers are arrested for the brutal murders of three little boys. Based on true events and the novel by Mara Leveritt.

title: Creation
description: From the writer of Master and Commander comes the inspirational story of how Charles Darwin created one of the most explosive ideas in history and became one of the greatest scientists the world has ever known. (2009)
description2: From the writer of Master and Commander comes the inspirational story of how Charles Darwin created one of the most explosive ideas in history and became one of the greatest scientists the world has ever known.

title: Primary Colours
description: An all star cast sees Governor Stanton as a presidential candidate who is devoted to the American people. With more than a few silent nods to Bill Clinton, this film is a look at power and corruption that cackles with humour. (1998)
description2: An all star cast sees Governor Stanton as a presidential candidate who is devoted to the American people. With more than a few silent nods to Bill Clinton, this film is a look at power and corruption that cackles with humour.

title: Murray Whelan: Stiff
description: Murray Whelan, a young political advisers, must play detective when he gets unwillingly dragged into a murder investigation as a body is found in the freezer. Based on a popular Australian series of detective books. (2004)
description2: Murray Whelan, a young political advisers, must play detective when he gets unwillingly dragged into a murder investigation as a body is found in the freezer. Based on a popular Australian series of detective books.

title: What's For Dinner? Lunar New Year (Simplified Chinese Subtitles)
episode_name: What's For Dinner? Lunar New Year (Simplified Chinese Subtitles)
description: Welcome to Penny's place for Lunar New Year! It starts with a race around the seafood markets for the freshest fish and veggies and ends with homemade dumplings, a colourful salad tossing tradition and some very cute dragons!

title: Songs of Praise: Enduring Hymns
description: Wynne Evans, Melanie Marshall, Wallingford Parish Church Choir and the congregation of Wesley Memorial Church in Oxford illustrate why hymns continue to inspire.
description2: Wynne Evans, Melanie Marshall, Wallingford Parish Church Choir and the congregation of Wesley Memorial Church in Oxford illustrate why hymns continue to inspire.
